# Data / artifacts (large, regenerable)
data/raw/
data/processed/
# Ignore results/ *contents* (not the dir) so the published baseline reports below
# can be re-included — a `results/` dir exclusion would make the negations below dead.
results/*
!results/baseline.html
!results/baseline.md
!results/baseline.jsonl
*.parquet
*.duckdb
*.sqlite

# Notebooks scratch
.ipynb_checkpoints/
